\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fsk1665703151779.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fsk1665703151779.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fsk1665703151779.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fsk1665703151779\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Returns a reference to the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span> object that contains the current object. Deprecated.\n   </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"fsk1665703151779__topic_d127754e1_d127755e1_d127756e1\">\n<div class=\"note important note_important\" id=\"fsk1665703151779__note_zpk_bh3_dwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Important:</span> The function <span class=\"keyword apiname\">getDSPInstance</span>\n        is deprecated. Use <span class=\"keyword apiname\">getInstance</span> instead. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jwv1665702534619.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jwv1665702534619.html\" title=\"Returns a reference to the uniface.Instance object that contains the current object.\">getInstance()</a>. </div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fsk1665703151779__p_d127757e1_d127758e1_d127759e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Object</var>.<span class=\"keyword apiname\">getDSPInstance()</span>\n</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fsk1665703151779__section_w1791ab1b5b3_w1792ab1b5_w1793ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d266890e86\">Arguments </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fsk1665703151779__section_w1794ab1b5b5_w1795ab1b5_w1796ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d266890e95\">Return Value</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fsk1665703151779__p_d127769e1_d127770e1_d127771e1\">Returns a reference to the\n               <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span> object.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fsk1665703151779__section_w1797ab1b5b7_w1798ab1b5_w1799ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d266890e107\">Exceptions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following exceptions may be thrown:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</code></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fsk1665703151779__section_byd_c4w_1dc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d266890e124\">Example: Using getInstance</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fsk1665703151779__p_d127778e1_d127779e1_d127780e1\">Using the <code class=\"ph codeph\">this</code> keyword to get the\n        current object, use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">getInstance</span> to get the parent component instance and\n        activate an operation.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104fsk1665703151779_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"fsk1665703151779__codeblock_pwh_233_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">this.getInstance().activate(\"myoperation\"); </code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/shk1665703139073.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</a><p>Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/reb1665702537007.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Entity</a><p>The uniface.Entity object provides access to selected properties of the component entity that it represents. It is returned by the getEntities and getEntity functions of the uniface.Instance and uniface.Occurrence objects.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hfh1665702535808.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Occurrence</a><p>The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dlx1665702535259.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Field</a><p>The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527645\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527645\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "getDSPInstance Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Returns a reference to the uniface.Instance object that contains the current object. Deprecated. Important: The function getDSPInstance is deprecated. Use getInstance instead. For more information, see getInstance() . Object . getDSPInstance() Arguments None Return Value Returns a reference to the uniface.Instance object. Exceptions The following exceptions may be thrown: uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Example: Using getInstance Using the this keyword to get the current object, use getInstance to get the parent component instance and activate an operation. Explain this code this.getInstance().activate(\"myoperation\"); Copy Related Links uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid. uniface.Entity The uniface.Entity object provides access to selected properties of the component entity that it represents. It is returned by the getEntities and getEntity functions of the uniface.Instance and uniface.Occurrence objects. uniface.Occurrence The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object. uniface.Field The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}